Definition: a state in which all hope is lost or absent
Example: in the depths of despair; they were rescued from despair at the last minute; courage born of desperation
Synonyms: verb, emotion, desperation, condition, a, state, in, which, all, hope, is, lost, or, absent, the, depths, of, they, were, rescued, from, at, last, minute, courage, born
Category: noun.state
